OL,3,C'We are still waiting for justice':
OL,4,CInfected blood victims call on PM to
OL,5,Cact
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has been challenged
OL,8,Fto give assurances to victims of the
OL,9,Finfected blood scandal that their
OL,10,F"suffering will not be dragged out
OL,11,Ffurther" amid ongoing concerns around
OL,12,Fthe compensation scheme.
OL,14,FIn a letter to Sir Keir Starmer,
OL,15,Fcampaigners have highlighted the
OL,16,F"physical and emotional burden" of the
OL,17,F"continual fight for fair
OL,18,Fcompensation".
