OL,7,FAnd more than 3,000 people have died
OL,8,Fas a result while survivors are living
OL,9,Fwith lifelong health implications.
OL,11,FA compensation scheme was announced
OL,12,Fthe day after the report was published.
OL,14,FThe Infected Blood Compensation
OL,15,FAuthority has said, as of May 6, 106
OL,16,Fcompensation payments have been made,
OL,17,Ftotalling more than #96 million.
