OL,7,FBut concerns have been raised about
OL,8,Fthe scheme, leading to the inquiry
OL,9,Fholding special hearings to highlight
OL,10,Fthe impact on victims.
OL,12,FThe new letter states: "The physical
OL,13,Fand emotional burden of this continual
OL,14,Ffight for fair compensation is falling
OL,15,Fwith ever greater weight on the
OL,16,Fshoulders of those who have already
OL,17,Fhad to campaign for too long."
