OL,3,C'We are still waiting for justice':
OL,4,CInfected blood victims call on PM to
OL,5,Cact
OL,7,F"We look to the Government now for
OL,8,Frecognition of the anxiety and stress
OL,9,Fthe last 12 months of uncertainty have
OL,10,Fcaused and for an assurance that this
OL,11,Fsuffering will not be dragged out
OL,12,Ffurther," adds the letter, which has
OL,13,Fbeen co-signed by officials from the
OL,14,FHaemophilia Society; Tainted Blood;
OL,15,FHaemophilia Wales; Haemophilia
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland and Tainted Blood `
OL,17,FAffected Siblings And Children.
