OL,3,C'We are still waiting for justice':
OL,4,CInfected blood victims call on PM to
OL,5,Cact
OL,7,FKate Burt, chief executive of the
OL,8,FHaemophilia Society, said: "A year
OL,9,Fago, the Infected Blood Inquiry
OL,10,Fpublished its devastating report into
OL,11,Fthe multiple failings that led to the
OL,12,Fcontaminated blood scandal.
OL,14,F"The inquiry gave us the truth but
OL,15,Fwe're still waiting for justice.
OL,17,F"Until everyone impacted by this
OL,18,Fscandal receives fair compensation,
OL,19,Fthere can be no justice.
