OL,3,C'We are still waiting for justice':
OL,4,CInfected blood victims call on PM to
OL,5,Cact
OL,7,F"Nor can justice be achieved without
OL,8,Flearning the lessons set out so
OL,9,Fcompellingly in the Infected Blood
OL,10,FInquiry's report.
OL,12,F"The steps taken towards implementing
OL,13,Fthe inquiry's recommendations are
OL,14,Fwelcome but there is a long road ahead.
OL,16,F"We urge the Government to make this a
OL,17,Fpriority for the safety and protection
OL,18,Fof everyone who uses the NHS today and
OL,19,Fin the future."
