OL,7,FThe letter adds: "The victims we work
OL,8,Fwith ` everyone with HIV ` should not
OL,9,Fbe burdened with further bureaucratic
OL,10,Fhurdles ` such as having to prove
OL,11,Fdiagnoses like 'full-blown AIDS' `
OL,12,Fnearly two decades of HIV without
OL,13,Ftreatment should speak for itself.
OL,15,F"Their claims are among the most
OL,16,Fstraightforward and should be
OL,17,Fprioritised accordingly."
