OL,4,CInfected blood victims call on PM to
OL,5,Cact
OL,7,FThe Paymaster General and Minister for
OL,8,Fthe Cabinet Office, Nick Thomas-
OL,9,FSymonds, said: "We are acting on the
OL,10,Finquiry's 12 recommendations, so that
OL,11,Fthis never happens again, and to get
OL,12,Fjustice for victims.
OL,14,F"While no amount of compensation will
OL,15,Fmake up for the suffering people have
OL,16,Fendured, we are committed to
OL,17,Fdelivering compensation as swiftly as
OL,18,Fpossible."
